102-275b @##/ /rgya gar skad du/ tri ku la maM ga la/ bod skad du/ rigs gsum gyi bkra shis/ dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo/ /bcom ldan gser mdog ri yi rgyal po 'dra/ /'jig rten gsum mgon 'jam dpal gzhon nu'i sku/ /bde gshegs sku yi bkra shis gang yin pa/ /bkra shis des ni deng 'dir bde legs shog /bcom ldan dung mdog ri yi rgyal po 'dra/ /'jig rten gsum mgon spyan ras gzigs kyi dbang / /bde gshegs gsung gi bkra shis gang yin pa/ /bkra shis des ni deng 'dir bde legs shog /bcom ldan ljang ser ri yi rgyal po 'dra/ /'jig rten gsum mgon phyag na rdo rje ste/ /bde gshegs thugs kyi bkra shis gang yin pa/ /bkra shis des ni deng 'dir bde legs shog /dpal rigs gsum gyi bkra shis rdzogs s+ho/ /
